article.description: — Setric Millner Jr. led a balanced attack with 17 points and Toledo defeated Cleveland St. 70-61 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Millner Jr. leads Toledo past Cleveland St. 70-61
article.linkText: Millner Jr. leads Toledo past Cleveland St. 70-61
article.story: TOLEDO, Ohio -- — Setric Millner Jr. led a balanced attack with 17 points and Toledo defeated Cleveland St. 70-61 on Tuesday night. Ryan Rollins had 15 points for Toledo (2-2), Marreon Jackson added 14 and Spencer Littleson 12. Jayson Woodrich had 13 points for the Vikings (0-1). Craig Beaudion added 12 points and Tre Gomillion had 11 points and eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
